cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a new approach for training deep neural networks that takes into account application-specific loss functions. This is a topic that is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR). However, given that the paper focuses on image and video analysis tasks, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
